snippet.textDisplay: Well here we are, #1000 is next. I bet some of you were surprised by me adding a Zelda track at 995 and now a Mario track at 999. I already said it, but #1000 is the track I always planned to end the list with (and that won't be the case now). I could have gone with the easy choices, but I have to be true to myself and keep it as a list of my own personal choice, just like how a Wild Arms track was #1. Even with the pressure of thousands of subscribers. I hope you guys understand.
